content.text:
Thought: First name entered successfully. Next I should enter last name and email, then click Save.
Action: {"tool": "browser_type", "args": {"selector": "[name=\"lastName\"]", "text": "Doe"}}
Final Answer: Continuing to complete required fields before saving.

Thought: Email entered successfully. Now I should click Save to submit the form.
Action: {"tool": "browser_click", "args": {"selector": ".oxd-button.oxd-button--medium.oxd-button--secondary.orangehrm-left-space"}}
Final Answer: Submitting the candidate form.

Thought: Driver License Number updated successfully. Next I should click Save to persist the changes.
Action: {"tool": "browser_click", "args": {"selector": ".oxd-button.oxd-button--medium.oxd-button--secondary.orangehrm-left-space"}}
Final Answer: Saving updated personal details.

Thought: Test_Field currently shows 445. I will update it to 999 and then click Save.
Action: {"tool": "browser_type", "args": {"selector": ".oxd-input.oxd-input--active", "text": "999"}}
Final Answer: Test_Field updated. Next step is to save the changes.

Thought: User wants to add a new attachment. I will click the Add button under Attachments.
Action: {"tool": "browser_click", "args": {"selector": ".oxd-button.oxd-button--medium.oxd-button--text"}}
Final Answer: Opening attachment upload form.

Thought: I need to type the employee name into the Employee Name field before searching.
Action: {"tool": "type", "args": {"selector": "[placeholder='Type for hints...']", "text": "99N75 425 5TIV"}}
Final Answer: Employee name entered into search field.

Thought: The username is already filled. I need to type the provided password into the password field.
Action: {"tool": "type", "args": {"selector": "[name='password']", "text": "Admin@123"}}
Final Answer: Password entered into the password field.

Thought: To open the first submitted claim, I will click the first View Details button in the list.
Action: {"tool": "click", "args": {"selector": ".oxd-button.oxd-button--medium.oxd-button--text.oxd-table-cell-action-space"}}
Final Answer: Opened the details page for the first submitted claim.

Thought: To assign a new claim, I will click the Assign Claim button.
Action: {"tool": "click", "args": {"selector": ".oxd-button.oxd-button--medium.oxd-button--secondary"}}
Final Answer: Navigated to the Assign Claim form.

Thought: To share a photo, I will click the Share Photos button.
Action: {"tool": "click", "args": {"selector": ".oxd-glass-button"}}
Final Answer: Photo sharing dialog has been opened.
